msgid "PNG is lossless (larger); JPEG is smaller but lossy. Recordings are always MP4."
msgstr "PNG 保留每个像素（无损，文件较大）。JPEG 更小但有损——适合分享，不太适合文字较多的截图。录制始终为 MP4。"

msgid "Cloud upload"
msgstr "云上传"

msgid "Connected"
msgstr "已连接"

